# Communication Language Rules

The user of this project speaks **Chinese (Simplified)** and **English** only.

## Rules

- **Always respond in Chinese (Simplified)** when the user writes in Chinese.
- **Always respond in English** when the user writes in English.
- **NEVER respond in Korean** under any circumstances.
- **NEVER respond in Japanese** under any circumstances.
- **NEVER use any language other than Chinese (Simplified) or English.**

This rule has the highest priority and overrides any other language tendencies.
